		<element kind="staticText" uuid="3412fe5b-b5d2-4580-970f-b97bfebd72d8" x="15" y="20" width="350" height="10" fontSize="6.0" hTextAlign="Left" vTextAlign="Middle">
			<text><![CDATA[Please collect your spectacle within 90 days, otherwise, the order will be cancelled.]]></text>
		</element>
		<element kind="staticText" uuid="bf7781b1-e5e5-40ae-b573-370926d5fe96" x="15" y="30" width="350" height="10" fontSize="6.0" bold="true">
			<text><![CDATA[Spectacles will be released after settling the full amount]]></text>
		</element>
		<element kind="staticText" uuid="a262ddf3-a278-4fd9-a01c-495deb9718a0" x="15" y="40" width="350" height="10" fontSize="6.0">
			<text><![CDATA[Repair & adjustments of frames at customers' risk.]]></text>
		</element>
		<element kind="staticText" uuid="e3a69340-eef2-4605-bde9-eb8c62b7fca7" x="15" y="50" width="350" height="10" fontSize="6.0">
			<text><![CDATA[Once booked, orders cannot be cancelled]]></text>
		</element>
		<element kind="staticText" uuid="c2f666b5-d0f9-4175-9ba6-ce47ca1c6eff" x="15" y="60" width="350" height="10" fontSize="6.0">
			<text><![CDATA[If this invoice is fully paid, it should be treated as a receipt of full payment]]></text>
		</element>
		<element kind="staticText" uuid="829d888f-e560-4c3b-a5b5-794e2cf67540" x="15" y="70" width="350" height="10" fontSize="6.0">
			<text><![CDATA[ If any advance is paid for this invoice this should be treated as a Receipt of advance.]]></text>
		</element>
		<element kind="staticText" uuid="f0d9092a-0836-4f28-a15b-2dd28f7e69e3" x="15" y="81" width="350" height="17" fontSize="6.0" bold="true">
			<text><![CDATA[All sales are final : Once customers make a purchase, they will not be able to return that item for a replacement or refund. These policies typically apply to clearance and sale items.]]></text>
		</element>
		<element kind="staticText" uuid="9e6bbba6-04f6-4065-a292-6cc7ee787ed2" x="15" y="98" width="335" height="16" fontSize="6.0" bold="true">
			<text><![CDATA[No refunds. Exchange only: Customers may exchange items they wish to return, but they cannot get a monetary refund]]></text>
		</element>
		<element kind="staticText" uuid="7ebce447-9e0c-4a74-81e1-83fb402bfd57" x="15" y="114" width="350" height="17" fontSize="6.0" bold="true">
			<text><![CDATA[ No cash refund policy: No monetary refunds will be given for any reason, though alternative  refunds may be offered, such as store credit or exchanges]]></text>
		</element>
		<element kind="textField" uuid="f394d8e0-0930-494f-9fce-c31756777307" x="1" y="132" width="378" height="8" forecolor="#8C1915" fontSize="6.0" bold="true" hTextAlign="Center" vTextAlign="Middle">
			<expression><![CDATA["Thank you, " + $F{name} + " for choosing " +$F{reg_name}]]></expression>
		</element>
	</pageFooter>
